title: 7 - Yedoye Travis

description: Yedoye Travis is taking back Ye, and he’s here with us this week to talk about everything from how our hometowns shape us to why old music doesn’t age well. You’ve seen him on Comedy Central, Epix, and Netflix’s Russian Doll, now hear him tell his tale. Here’s five words to describe this episode: he’s truly taking back Ye.
